official_title: A concurrent resolution authorizing the printing of "Background Materials Concerning Child and Family Services Act".

summary.text: (Reported to House from the Committee on House Administration with amendment, H. Rept. 94-1411) Authorizes the printing of 25,000 additional copies of the committee print entitled "Background Materials Concerning Child and Family Services Act, 1975 (S. 626)." Directs that such copies shall be for the use of the Senate Committee on Labor and Public Welfare. Authorizes the printing of 100,000 additional copies of the committee print entitled "Background Materials Concerning Child and Family Services Act, 1975, (H.R. 2966). Directs that such copies shall be for the use of the House Committee on Education and Labor.
